"""
NVFS — Public Trait Contracts

@tag:stdlib
@tag:api

Trait surface for the NVMe-aware filesystem (SimpleFS-NV / NVFS). Sibling
of `fs/path.spl`. Concrete impls live in submodule `examples/nvfs/`.

Submodules:
  - api:             arena_* trait alias (delegates to std.storage.arena).
  - extent_map:      `ExtentMapEntry` + `ExtentMap` trait.
  - superblock_if:   `SuperblockReader` trait skeleton.

Shared primitives (StorageClass, Capability, ArenaHandle, DurabilityClass)
live in `src/lib/nogc_sync_mut/storage/` and are imported by NVFS callers
directly — NVFS does NOT re-export them to avoid duplicate public symbols.

See:
  - doc/05_design/nvfs_design.md §2 (MDSOC), §3 (classes), §4 (arena_*), §6 (capabilities)
  - doc/05_design/nvfs/from_spostgre.md
